claim: Flublok ensures identical antigenic match with WHO- and FDA-selected flu strains.
explanation: A CONSORT-style flow diagram showing participant enrollment and disposition: 4648 subjects enrolled and randomized (2344 to FluBlok, 2304 to placebo), with numbers of discontinuations and resulting safety populations for each group. The figure does not include any information on antigenic matching or strain selection; it simply details subject enrollment and disposition, so it does not support the claim.
